{"tid":1663089,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"潘女與陳女之死 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-10-19T07:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T08:00:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"576e6b867c3ffa88333f44776cf3335a1bdd44c8","tid":1663089,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191018/20788831/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788831%2F&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoN9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=1e9b2773\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788831%2F&h=be895130\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191018/20788831/</a><br />\n<br />\n潘女與陳女之死 - 陳也<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191018/large/1571301871_64c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191018%2Flarge%2F1571301871_64c6.jpg&h=a01a43bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15歲彥霖入讀那家知專，過去幾日擠牙膏式發放訊息，陰謀啲諗，院校跟黑警有仇，扣起閉路電視，學黨鐵陰招，等大家鎖定仇恨，入黑警數。咁係幾高章嘅！可是知專管理處發英文信給員工，跟黑警同一口徑用曱甴形容示威者，唔使審，良心在太子站警署外跌咗。咁大間學院，過百台閉路電視，學校蓄意拖延俾人睇足本，刺激示威者大舉裝修。要查吓保安是否退役警員，行埋林志偉，放水讓速龍入來拉人，撳頸仆頭，好快紅過禿sir！<br />\n<br />\n七個月前林奠引用惡法所謂的初心，源於港男在台北殺害潘姓女友，台發放閉路電視緝兇，潘母向民&times;聯哭訴，林奠跳出來口口聲聲為死者父母尋公義，祭出逃犯修訂條例，炒到香港遍地開花！林奠對待陳女與潘女，公義那把尺何以不一樣，大家心照。四個月下來抗爭者硬食警暴迫害，可疑浮屍被警方快速定性為無可疑，問誰能為15歲彥霖的亡靈解畫？還原真相只有3cm距離，學校卻以盧偉聰「指膊為肺」做榜樣，不惜代價，寧做幫兇。陳母自言唔想搞大件事，如屬自殺，點搞都唔會大。除非陳母被慈母忠告：利用潘女送中整唔瓜香港，用陳女引緊急法一定煮死香港！ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"cafe09aeca62021ae3f65e0e85517c7cb58bb22d","tid":1663089,"uid":51806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho9fQPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho9fQPQ.jpg&h=4f50251a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3AnpJ9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AnpJ9R.jpg&h=c15a6527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmfOrod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmfOrod.jpg&h=017db543&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2994de04adbc34ad7f66dc258350132e5650d865","tid":1663089,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span> <br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n日期：10月20日<br />\n時間： 1330 <br />\n地點：梳士巴利花園<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n[已獲不反對通知書]"}]}